  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Supervisior",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage customer complaints and communicate effectively to resolve conflicts</li>\n  <li>Manage manpower deployment and arrange overtime when the need arises</li>\n  <li>Ensures all goods in warehouse are properly collected, received, accurately sorted, identified, transferred and dispatched</li>\n  <li>Handle day to day operational, safety and quality issues</li>\n  <li>Assign tasks to staff and scheduling</li>\n  <li>Overall management of the logistics administration and documentation</li>\n  <li>Ensure staff compliance to all established processes and accuracy in data processing</li>\n  <li>Any other assigned duties in the warehouse as instructed by superior</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Specific Accountabilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ensures Health and Safety compliance in accordance with company polices</li>\n  <li>Hands-on experience in storekeeping will be an added advantage</li>\n  <li>Ability to deal with all levels of people</li>\n  <li>Able to perform work with minimal supervision</li>\n  <li>Accuracy and speed in performing daily activities</li>\n</ul>",
